{"tha-ap501:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap501:0.2":"Kinkanipupphavagga ","tha-ap501:0.3":"9 Nalakutidayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap501:1.1":"“Himavantassavidure, ","tha-ap501:1.2":"harito nama pabbato; ","tha-ap501:1.3":"Sayambhu narado nama, ","tha-ap501:1.4":"rukkhamule vasi tada. ","tha-ap501:2.1":"Nalagaram karitvana, ","tha-ap501:2.2":"tinena chadayim aham; ","tha-ap501:2.3":"Cankamam sodhayitvana, ","tha-ap501:2.4":"sayambhussa adasaham. ","tha-ap501:3.1":"Tena kammena sukatena, ","tha-ap501:3.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","tha-ap501:3.3":"Jahitva manusam deham, ","tha-ap501:3.4":"tavatimsamagacchaham. ","tha-ap501:4.1":"Tattha me sukatam byamham, ","tha-ap501:4.2":"nalakutikanimmitam; ","tha-ap501:4.3":"Satthiyojanamubbedham, ","tha-ap501:4.4":"timsayojanavitthatam. ","tha-ap501:5.1":"Catuddasesu kappesu, ","tha-ap501:5.2":"devaloke ramim aham; ","tha-ap501:5.3":"Ekasattatikkhattunca, ","tha-ap501:5.4":"devarajjamakarayim. ","tha-ap501:6.1":"Catutimsatikkhattunca, ","tha-ap501:6.2":"cakkavatti ahosaham; ","tha-ap501:6.3":"Padesarajjam vipulam, ","tha-ap501:6.4":"gananato asankhiyam. ","tha-ap501:7.1":"Dhammapasadamaruyha, ","tha-ap501:7.2":"sabbakaravarupamam; ","tha-ap501:7.3":"Yadicchakaham vihare, ","tha-ap501:7.4":"sakyaputtassa sasane. ","tha-ap501:8.1":"Ekatimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap501:8.2":"yam kammamakarim tada; ","tha-ap501:8.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap501:8.4":"nalakutiyidam phalam. ","tha-ap501:9.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap501:9.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap501:9.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap501:10.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap501:10.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap501:10.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap501:11.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap501:11.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap501:11.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap501:12.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma nalakutidayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap501:13.1":"Nalakutidayakattherassapadanam navamam. "}